{
  "stem": "7093.8",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "And one of them was-- and that, that was when I had enough-- when he, during the night, he started to threaten me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "I woke up that he was trying to kill me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "Because then they would kill him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "Then they would kill him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "And then I moved out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "And I moved, moved somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "I came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "I had a job by that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "I was already working at the American Joint Distribution Committee as a filing-- as a [INAUDIBLE] first, and then-- anyway, very badly paid.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 100,
      "text": "We-- I just earned enough for one person to live on badly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 101,
      "text": "But for two people, it was really pretty desperate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 102,
      "text": "And we-- I was constantly hungry again and was really in a very bad state.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 103,
      "text": "And, and also, I, I was terrified.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 104,
      "text": "And I've moved out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 105,
      "text": "I didn't sleep there anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 106,
      "text": "But I came back and did his, did his cooking and did his washing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 107,
      "text": "And he-- eventually, I got him on to the boat to South Africa.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 108,
      "text": "And then he went to South Africa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 109,
      "text": "And he broke down on the boat completely again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 110,
      "text": "So when he arrived in South Africa, they gave him-- he couldn't take quite a job.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 111,
      "text": "But he could play, could play.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 112,
      "text": "And they gave him a, a, a black student to look after him, to shave him, to wash him and bring him to the, to the rehearsal or to the concert.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 113,
      "text": "And then when-- once he sat down, he played beautifully.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 114,
      "text": "So he was all right in that way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 115,
      "text": "They could use him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 116,
      "text": "But-- and then he made-- he told stories about me, that his wife is coming out, who was in Auschwitz and whose nails were torn out.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 117,
      "text": "And all kinds of stories, he, he started telling about me.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
